Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 真讓人著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋樣 我的GExes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…覺得和高達有幾分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相似 相似
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在乎小事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達Titus確實厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GExes也絲毫不落下風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 宇宙雖大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這種手藝的機動戰士工匠著實不多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出是一頂一的高手所造
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰造了這台GExes？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 別那麼一本正經的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有約會邀請嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有魅力的男人真忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是沃爾夫·安尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是麥德納大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始移居殖民衛星後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷經數百年宇宙時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭奪地球圈霸權的戰爭終於偃旗息鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的時代似乎降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和平卻如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現的不明敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令一顆殖民衛星化作宇宙的塵埃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這將成為百年漫長戰爭的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有正常一點的駕駛方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 那就是麥德納工坊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造GExes的牛逼大叔就住那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫先生 要撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到站了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小瞧前賽車手的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 軍用機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在未經聯邦認可的設施進行改裝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是違法的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 也有許多我這樣的排隊來買
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是看重這裏老闆的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是個出了名的倔脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們 到時候別後悔跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想毀了我的工坊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事才急著來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意 進來吧沃爾夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拉拉帕裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為你這麼慣著沃爾夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子才爬鼻子上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收聲！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最經常損壞工坊是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次 讓研製中的等離子炮爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牆壁破了那麼大一個窟窿以為我會不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢碰上老婆也沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒轍 沒轍 沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說這些 有東西想給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來工廠區
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 這裏就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組裝工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管不是軍隊的工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有這麼先進的設備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想讓爺爺看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既有聯邦軍的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有從未見過的機型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還是經過整體改裝的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多里面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能找到適合我的機動戰士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適合 適合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是玩具 誰允許你碰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 怎麼帶來這麼一群吵吵鬧鬧的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們對老爹的敬仰之情如滔滔江水…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係 讓孩子們看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正這裏的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全～是你個人愛好造的試作機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試作機？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了給沃爾夫做機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他別提多激動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不能輸給那個叫高達的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也要造出更強更有型的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GExes果然是仿高達造的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 GExes的品質完全無可挑剔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅擁有高功率光束軍刀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大幅提升近身戰鬥能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝卸式的盾牌還可以作為輔助裝甲強化防禦力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有了這些我感覺完全不輸給高達
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可動軸的轉向速度方面高達完全佔優
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機構關節的柔韌性和緩震性能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是高達的效率較高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明日野家的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣我有話想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這裏的協調控制系統…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人為什麼都那麼傻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家這位更是特大號的機動戰士傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿他沒法子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我家老爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺是高達機械工程師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也說GExes的製造者是一頂一的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工程師之間 有某些共通的語言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是個好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說 我也是被那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為某件事廢寢忘食的樣子迷上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那麼相親相愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說老爹 剛才的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事讓你在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你不說我都給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 UE的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這東西會在老爹機庫裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請解釋是怎麼回事 麥德納先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據回答 就算是老爹…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事出有因的話請告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張 二位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這台機動戰士是受某位客戶所托
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運送到這裏來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作是 提升這東西的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個客戶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個客戶是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 艾米莉 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一知道的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去大家都得翹辮子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥德納先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請借給我們能用的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去用格納庫裏的Shaldoll
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別輕敵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙打算逃去外面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往哪裏逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損失情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在確認中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先救人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上顯示畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫先生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過這麼鋒利的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我引誘它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去喊高達
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 聽得見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動高達
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和UE的機動戰士交戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 艦長點頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就來 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:12:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉體在宇宙空間裏 最多只能呆15秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記出去前吐完肺裏的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太瘋狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背對太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對速度匹配
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你小子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟不上對方的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台新的重量級高達
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不適合對付高速型的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把背露給它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這樣下去贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟上它的速度…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系統…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 翻新了還是老樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是那傢伙佔盡上風
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他結束這樣的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是菲利特堅持要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然明白是為了大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束是讓他逃避戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣是為他好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是做得挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃避任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果真的為他著想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他豁出性命去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就豁出性命去跟著他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豁出性命…跟著他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡他吧 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的話 就和他生死相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是遙控 就是自動駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可能是 機師潛伏在裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台機體混身都是謎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以肯定的是 那是UE的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 話說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說過武器商人亞庫·多勒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞庫·多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個人 把那台黑色機體送到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出的報酬也數額不菲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:15:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始還興奮了一陣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它和其他機動戰士的設計思想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差異過大讓人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在調查開發來源的過程中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了一條聯邦的機密情報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了那台機體和聯邦戰鬥的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明它曾經是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以聯繫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺中被UE利用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在沒臉見人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別怪我老公
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是毫不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況我們明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 武器商人竟然和UE有勾結
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我也不知道更多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果亞庫·多勒受雇於UE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要找出他 就能知道UE的真面目了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 回到天神號上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞庫·多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這個名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:17:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說向法丁倒賣機動戰士設計圖的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是此人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天後從法丁出發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個目的地是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星托爾迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地變更
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星 明斯利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 請解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們人類 對UE殘虐的破壞忍氣吞聲到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不能讓暴行再繼續下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對迄今為止的數據進行分析
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於得出結論
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE就潛伏在附近的廢棄宇宙要塞安巴德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可錯過這次良機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦將與艾烏巴艦兩艘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及扎拉姆艦兩艘組成聯合艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向UE據點實施攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說也太蠻幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和聯邦軍以外的私兵組編
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總司令部不可能認可！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍無關緊要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中是有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞當斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你知道請告訴我們 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了前任艦長的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是瘋狂的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要抽出衛星軸心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓天神號牽引住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不會聽他的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓天神號立即撤離危險的諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 如果是前任艦長的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉的人們現在已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我當時不知該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 現在知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克先生做的事是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還是那個艦長的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉的人會被拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都會死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個戴安·馮羅德的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實難保不會那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果沒有古魯迪克艦長的決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號也沒法戰鬥到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫先生 蜜蕾絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你做的事是嚴重的違紀行為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為軍人罪不可恕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已被聯邦軍作為叛逃者追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這一切都是為了擊敗UE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克先生的家人被UE殺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨UE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使隕落之日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一切的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妻女被UE所殺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女兒莎拉年僅7歲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 我就發誓向UE復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 中校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我們陪你去報私仇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 不打算強迫大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和我共同行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會被聯邦軍認定為叛逃者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有想下船的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就下船無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算一個人也要去幹翻UE！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 這場戰鬥會異常艱苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法保證能活著回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父親和母親也被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 我會和古魯迪克先生一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睜睜看著UE奪走身邊的家人和朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都給你小子搶著說完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡主動找UE麻煩的傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍再大也找不到第二個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有通訊員 天神號寸步難行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說 我也想痛扁UE那群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是天神號上的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敵系統反應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.40,0:21:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到眾多類UE移動體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 對面送上門來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:22:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來UE動真格想幹掉我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理準備嗎 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.11,0:22:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 一級戰鬥準備
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.38,0:22:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起豁出性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.43,0:22:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蜂擁而至的敵人大軍面前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士們拋棄過節團結一心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.56,0:24:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.15,0:24:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激戰之日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.53,0:24:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.44,0:24:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有脫離聯邦接受機動戰士改裝委託的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.90,0:24:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由機械工程師聯合組織
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.83,0:24:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中享有盛名的是麥德納工坊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.85,0:24:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼機動戰士來到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會被改裝成最佳狀態

